libldb-devel、python3-ldb、python-ldb-devel-common、libldb-help、python3-ldb-devel、libldb
·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP3 2403
·aarch64架构:
libldb-devel、python3-ldb、python-ldb-devel-common、libldb-help、python3-ldb-devel、libldb
